==Introduction==

===Abstract===

This document redefines <code>OP_NOP4</code> (<code>0xB3</code>) in Tapscript ([[bip-0342.mediawiki|BIP 342]]) as <code>OP_CHECKSPHINCSVERIFY</code> for verifying bitcoin-optimized SPHINCS+ signatures carried in the Taproot annex, which is the optional <code>0x50</code>-prefixed witness element defined in [[bip-0341.mediawiki|BIP 341]].

The annex may contain multiple signatures, enabling per-tapleaf multisignature constructs via Taproot MAST. The design supports hybrid Schnorr plus post-quantum scripts as a gradual migration path: non-upgraded nodes treat <code>OP_NOP4</code> as a no-op and still validate all Schnorr signature checks in the same script, while upgraded nodes additionally enforce SPHINCS+ verification.

